{"id": "ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 1050, "displayName": {"text": "Bumsan Organic Milk Bar", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Cheery, mod pink-hued stop for soft-serve ice cream with customizable toppings, sprinkles & cones.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWTFYwRTFVRWxPZEMxMFExSlVaV05QTTJVemRYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "One of my favorite K-town treats! I have loved every flavor I've tried so far. The classic milk flavor on a cone (with sugar sprinkles on the rim, duh!) and rainbow sprinkles on top is my go to fave if I need a special pick-me-up! ", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of my favorite K-town treats! I have loved every flavor I've tried so far. The classic milk flavor on a cone (with sugar sprinkles on the rim, duh!) and rainbow sprinkles on top is my go to fave if I need a special pick-me-up! ", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rebecca K. Shipman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109206355411168489775/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXK0QU_QKFoeLVRE7yLDmeBbvFgG4IeOe7G1ZceUQQuhpu17n0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-25T07:18:02.640512834Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWTFYwRTFVRWxPZEMxMFExSlVaV05QTTJVemRYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWTFYwRTFVRWxPZEMxMFExSlVaV05QTTJVemRYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b89af9d56399:0x122f256dee0bf04e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paVWJXeHVMWEJ5YlcwMWJEbHBjRVZFZG1SalJFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I ordered the taro milk and strawberry cream soft serve. I’d definitely come back for the taro! Unfortunately, they were out of croffles around 9 pm, so I’ll have to return to try them.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I ordered the taro milk and strawberry cream soft serve. I’d definitely come back for the taro! Unfortunately, they were out of croffles around 9 pm, so I’ll have to return to try them.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sneha Jain", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111985761449740233458/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCUDanyE6YY6yQFl1gjdUKkP02mYbOiGKrCT4hE6IFB_234Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-16T01:12:06.105131180Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paVWJXeHVMWEJ5YlcwMWJEbHBjRVZFZG1SalJFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paVWJXeHVMWEJ5YlcwMWJEbHBjRVZFZG1SalJFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b89af9d56399:0x122f256dee0bf04e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1dWNVUm9WSE5tYkhoamVUTnlWR001YVhGVlMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "This ice‑cream shop has changed over time, and unfortunately it’s gone from being one of my favorite spots to grab a treat to feeling like just an average ice‑cream shop.\n\nFirst, they swapped out one of their best topping options — the simple, crunchy cornflakes — for a rainbow fruity‑pebbles–style topping. For a place that advertises organic ice‑cream, this choice feels completely off‑brand. Those colorful flakes are almost guaranteed to contain artificial dyes and flavorings, which contradicts the whole “organic” concept. On top of that, the topping is overly sweet and has such a strong flavor that it overpowers the ice‑cream unless you’re eating a very neutral flavor like vanilla. It’s just not a good match.\n\nAnd now, the biggest disappointment: they removed their best flavor, Taro, and replaced it with mango. Taro was unique, subtle, and one of the main reasons this shop stood out from the crowd. Mango is fine — it’s sweet and enjoyable — but it doesn’t compare as a replacement. Taro had a gentle sweetness that was satisfying without being overwhelming. Losing it takes away a lot of what made this place special.\n\nPlease bring Taro back. 😫😢", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This ice‑cream shop has changed over time, and unfortunately it’s gone from being one of my favorite spots to grab a treat to feeling like just an average ice‑cream shop.\n\nFirst, they swapped out one of their best topping options — the simple, crunchy cornflakes — for a rainbow fruity‑pebbles–style topping. For a place that advertises organic ice‑cream, this choice feels completely off‑brand. Those colorful flakes are almost guaranteed to contain artificial dyes and flavorings, which contradicts the whole “organic” concept. On top of that, the topping is overly sweet and has such a strong flavor that it overpowers the ice‑cream unless you’re eating a very neutral flavor like vanilla. It’s just not a good match.\n\nAnd now, the biggest disappointment: they removed their best flavor, Taro, and replaced it with mango. Taro was unique, subtle, and one of the main reasons this shop stood out from the crowd. Mango is fine — it’s sweet and enjoyable — but it doesn’t compare as a replacement. Taro had a gentle sweetness that was satisfying without being overwhelming. Losing it takes away a lot of what made this place special.\n\nPlease bring Taro back. 😫😢", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Charlene Crudup", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110213877889520450367/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVR9bEh5qkfqaICGoagAxYqjqQY5ytqpjioOw9p50qSMUYOg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T14:07:43.946914888Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1dWNVUm9WSE5tYkhoamVUTnlWR001YVhGVlMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1dWNVUm9WSE5tYkhoamVUTnlWR001YVhGVlMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b89af9d56399:0x122f256dee0bf04e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SamVXRjJXV0Z0UkVWZlEyb3dkREpLZGpoNFdsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "11 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "The ice cream was good but melted the minute we held it, this are didn’t have AC felt bad for the person working there because it’s such a tiny shop seating area is outside. They  have a few ice cream flavors that do taste good but they had limited toppings. I had the Korean coffee and it was amazing with the rice crispy cone 10/10.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The ice cream was good but melted the minute we held it, this are didn’t have AC felt bad for the person working there because it’s such a tiny shop seating area is outside. They  have a few ice cream flavors that do taste good but they had limited toppings. I had the Korean coffee and it was amazing with the rice crispy cone 10/10.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Thando Malinga", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106999171552199194085/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU12uz0aQ52YJ7j91_A7mvcRwUXTYnkFGRCejR-oURNZiE_5cHu=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-02T03:20:50.627077195Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SamVXRjJXV0Z0UkVWZlEyb3dkREpLZGpoNFdsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SamVXRjJXV0Z0UkVWZlEyb3dkREpLZGpoNFdsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b89af9d56399:0x122f256dee0bf04e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKSFZGSkxaVzlRUkVSeWNuSjFVVUkxTWpCelMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I got the Croffle – Soulmate and milk ice cream. The croffle was nice and crispy, and the ice cream was perfectly sweet and super smooth. I went with Oreo topping. There’s always a line, so I was curious—and now I get why. So good! 😋", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got the Croffle – Soulmate and milk ice cream. The croffle was nice and crispy, and the ice cream was perfectly sweet and super smooth. I went with Oreo topping. There’s always a line, so I was curious—and now I get why. So good! 😋", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "박밍또", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111570459748618867897/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2pmmztVuSR1DcrFlBfIyfWOdFVQ3qOy7PCDf3ts5o4RVNij8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-20T20:42:31.516762820Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKSFZGSkxaVzlRUkVSeWNuSjFVVUkxTWpCelMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKSFZGSkxaVzlRUkVSeWNuSjFVVUkxTWpCelMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b89af9d56399:0x122f256dee0bf04e"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJmWPV-Zq4woARTvAL7m0lLxI/photos/AWCwydgAumqiieYQ1Do5PTQp2S1JJ-V4ynNitKOvAP0A0YlUFXGTdOnt4HjIF2dOrybWCYElEslnc_reDDu6QAPdzjo0NKpzM-Jvk0OrKyFUKnL8vytkJBF4t-ym0ZCc3xybmjoBeMhHrmWcfxuBwYvZxZqySyFaCJv6KZH6zLwZLECU6tLiIkuUZ6ECrnNNG5T_p6OkTe2fDBLIEiaA9GdxXuiUlDsHutn5Kx5ndsH1Uw9tLo3VVJZ2anyXYJm_d3q-SCt7JAPhNJ9D7emXC2D_3dXmQx0vNWGN2hPltWyr52My8Ri7_ZLizvT_LhlbCbiYKw0yeR46vFEmDLf3UMCDTmpPs5wgLw9fQk-7WVSfM1XHlDr4EnPKLeO-bWvu6CmnQ52k4dfxC-NwUUQdPpR4j_PC4IJgXJZ8rIrGGkl_y1mwxvseI-qaW5jhnyvY3bU2", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttribut